.container
  .row.row--intro
    .col-6.d-flex__vertical-align
      %h1.mb-4(style="width:800px")
        Automate buying <br />
        Bitcoin
        %span.db-anim-rotator
          %span.db-anim-rotator--1 hourly
          %span.db-anim-rotator--2 daily
          %span.db-anim-rotator--3 weekly
      %p
        Five-minute setup. Works with exchanges. <br/> Fully automated. Saves money and time.
      %p
        The basic version is
        %b.text-success.text-success--lighter free
        forever.

      %a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg.my-2.my-sm-0.mt-4.mt-sm-4{:href => new_user_registration_path}
        %span.mr-2 Get started
        %i.material-icons-round arrow_forward
    .col-6.db-intro-image-container
      %img.db-intro-image{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/bot.png")}
  .row.db-infoblocks.text-white
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.db-infoblocks__item
      %p
        %img.db-lineart--home{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/lineart_proven_strategy.svg")}
      %h5 Proven strategy
      %p <b><i>Dollar-cost averaging</i></b> (DCA) is&nbsp;a well-known and recommended strategy of longterm&nbsp;investing.
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.db-infoblocks__item
      %p
        %img.db-lineart--home{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/lineart_mitigate_risk.svg")}
      %h5 Mitigate risk
      %p Automate buying small chunks on&nbsp;a&nbsp;regular schedule to get a&nbsp;fair price without stress.
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.db-infoblocks__item
      %p
        %img.db-lineart--home{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/lineart_set_forget.svg")}
      %h5 Set and forget
      %p All you need is an exchange account and a few minutes for&nbsp;setting the bot up.
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.db-infoblocks__item
      %p
        %img.db-lineart--home{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/lineart_smart_intervals.svg")}
      %h5 Unique implementation
      %p To get the best results, we use our <i>smart intervals</i> approach. Log in to read more.

  .row.db-has-chart-art
    %img.db-chart-art{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/chart.svg")}
    .col-6.db-dca-info
      %h2 Why dollar-cost averaging?
      %p
        DCA is an easy-to-follow strategy that helps to manage emotions and risk of investing in volatile assets. Don't try to time the market. Buy&nbsp;small amounts on a fixed schedule, and get an average price. With&nbsp;automation, it gets more accessible than ever before.
    .col-6
  .db-row--how-does-it-work
    %h2.my-4.text-white How does it work?

    .row.db-infoblocks.text-white
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.db-infoblocks__item
        %p
          %img.db-lineart--home{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/lineart_exchange.svg")}
        %h5 Login to your exchange
        %p Deltabadger works with selected cryptoexchanges. Currently, we support Kraken and Bitbay.
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.db-infoblocks__item
        %p
          %img.db-lineart--home{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/lineart_api_keys.svg")}
        %h5 Get API keys
        %p No worries, we walk you through the process. It's safe: the keys have limited permissions.
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.db-infoblocks__item
        %p
          %img.db-lineart--home{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/lineart_set_up.svg")}
        %h5 Five-minute setup
        %p Enter your API keys. Choose the desired schedule. Press <b>Start</b>. Done.
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3.db-infoblocks__item
        %p
          %img.db-lineart--home{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/lineart_track_it.svg")}
        %h5 Track results
        %p The fun part. It's very satisfying to check how your investment performs over time.

  .row.db-supported-exchanges
    .col-12
      %h4.text-white.mb-4 Currently supported exchanges:
    .col-12
      %img.db-supported-exchange{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/bitbay-white.svg")}
      %img.db-supported-exchange{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/kraken-white.svg")}

  .row.row--newsletter
    .col-lg-6.pb-4
      %h2.mb-4 Waitâ€¦ it's more!
      %p We're working on a unique set of tools for investors and traders focused on risk management. Stay in touch if you're interested.
      #newsletter
    .col-lg-6.pb-4.d-flex__vertical-align
      %img.db-art.db-art--newsletter{:src => asset_pack_path("media/images/art-newsletter.svg")}
